sources.title: Woman Unafraid (1934) LONA ANDRE
sources.description:
EXCLUSIVE Movie Class PizzaFLIX Edition!
Stars: Lucile Gleason, Lona Andre, Jason Robards, Sr.

An aging policewoman vows to keep the dance halls on her beat free from a dangerous gangster!

metadata.Plot: After putting away a gangster, a policewoman tries to turn around the lives of several young women with shady pasts.
